videos.headline: Singletary puts Owls in red zone
videos.description: Devin Singletary takes the handoff and finds an opening over the middle for a 47-yard gain.

videos.headline: Florida Atlantic's Solomon hits wide open Franklin for reverse TD
videos.description: WR Kamrin Solomon takes the toss and finds John Franklin III open on the outside for a 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Woods breaks out for long gain on reverse
videos.description: FAU's John Franklin III hands it off to Kalib Woods, who fakes the double reverse and breaks out for a 49-yard gain.

videos.headline: Driskel connects with Woods for long gain
videos.description: FAU's Jason Driskel completes a pass over the middle to Kalib Wood for a 44-yard gain in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Woods reels in sideline grab
videos.description: FAU's Jacob Driskel airs it out down the sidelines to Kalib Woods for a 34-yard gain.

videos.headline: Singletary starts off 2nd quarter with TD
videos.description: On the first play of the second quarter, Devin Singletary takes the handoff to the outside for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Driskel finds Solomon for big gain
videos.description: FAU's Jason Driskel connects with Kamrin Solomon over the middle for a 51-yard reception.

videos.headline: FAU's Young picks off Fine in the end zone
videos.description: North Texas QB Mason Fine forces a pass into the end zone and it's picked off by Jalen Young.

videos.headline: Singletary breaks tackle for TD
videos.description: FAU's Devin Singletary takes the handoff to the outside and shakes off a defender for the 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kiffin: 'I don't like how we are in the red zone'
videos.description: Despite FAU leading North Texas 27-0 at halftime, head coach Lane Kiffin isn't satisfied and wants his team to play better.

videos.headline: FAU's Al-ShaairHear lays big hit on return
videos.description: Azeez Al-ShaairHear trucks over Evan Johnson on the kick return in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Woods surpasses 200 receiving yards with TD
videos.description: Jason Driskel connects with Kalib Woods down the sideline for a 54-yard touchdown, giving Woods over 200 receiving yards for the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Woods surpasses 200 receiving yards with TD) 2017/12/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fine airs it out for 77-yard North Texas TD
videos.description: Mean Green QB Mason Fine lets it fly over the middle to Turner Smiley for a 77-yard touchdown in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fine airs it out for 77-yard North Texas TD) 2017/12/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Singletary's 29th TD ties C-USA record
videos.description: Devin Singletary rushes for his 29th touchdown of the season, tying him with Kevin Smith for the Conference USA single-season record.

videos.headline: FAU's Franklin drops ball short of end zone
videos.description: Florida Atlantic WR John Franklin III's touchdown is overturned after he dropped the ball short of the goal line during the Conference USA championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (FAU's Franklin drops ball short of end zone) 2017/12/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: FAU coasts by North Texas to claim C-USA title
videos.description: Devin Singletary runs for 164 yards and three touchdowns to help Florida Atlanta win the Conference USA championship with a 41-17 victory over North Texas.
